<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">有杕之杜</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsondbb89539e933">
<p>有杕之杜，生于道左。彼君子兮，噬肯适我？中心好之，曷饮食之？</p>
<p>有杕之杜，生于道周。彼君子兮，噬肯来游？中心好之，曷饮食之？</p>
</div>
</div>
